    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >当冰层不断融化，北极熊的回家之路将变得越来越艰难⋯⋯</h2><br>《极地乐园》是一款以北极冰洋为背景的<strong>益智解谜游戏</strong>，你将规划一条条顺畅的路线，引领北极熊回到小熊的身旁。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713140/extras/afd84c30a947eff4b0e1b3ab0e493cb6.poster.avif?t=1729047149\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713140/extras/afd84c30a947eff4b0e1b3ab0e493cb6.webm?t=1729047149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713140/extras/afd84c30a947eff4b0e1b3ab0e493cb6.mp4?t=1729047149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>10 几种独特的地图机制交织成<strong> 150 个</strong>精心设计的关卡。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713140/extras/4fd742b0e582ec8045a4eb5476242216.avif?t=1729047149\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br></li><li>仔细斟酌每一步，因为逐渐融化的冰块将减少你的下一步选择。<br>不限时、无压力、不用追求高分、可以随时悔棋或前往别关。静心体验每一个挑战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713140/extras/a283aafec2c5c4dfea35b9073b509569.poster.avif?t=1729047149\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713140/extras/a283aafec2c5c4dfea35b9073b509569.webm?t=1729047149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713140/extras/a283aafec2c5c4dfea35b9073b509569.mp4?t=1729047149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>可爱的小熊、海豹、海鹦！沉浸在冷冽的极地氛围与童趣的绘本风格中，横渡冰洋。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713140/extras/dbe9423c0fafa747294a02264222668c.poster.avif?t=1729047149\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713140/extras/dbe9423c0fafa747294a02264222668c.webm?t=1729047149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713140/extras/dbe9423c0fafa747294a02264222668c.mp4?t=1729047149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </li></ul>",
